Sequence Information.Source: Skin Secretion of the African Frog, Kassina senegalensis
Sequence Information.Target Organism: Tumor cells:NCI-H460 (IC50=1.67 μM); NCI-H838 (IC50=10.3 μM); U-251MG (IC50=13.20 μM ); NCI-H157 (IC50=21.54 μM); LNCaP (IC50=3.79 μM); NCI-H23 (IC50=4.52 μM)
Sequence Information.Hemolytic Activity: Human RBCs:Kassinatuerin-3 produced no detectable hemolysis activity up to a concentration of 160 μM

Literature.Title: A Novel Antimicrobial Peptide (Kassinatuerin-3) Isolated from the Skin Secretion of the African Frog, Kassina senegalensis
